      "span_text": "As a final set of experiments, we also compare the results of the above proposed MPS algorithm with the quadratically constrained quadratic program (QCQP) and SDP-based methods for synchronization with anchors introduced in and reviewed in Appendix B, when the adjacency graph of available pairwise measurements is an Erdős-Rényi graph G(n, α) with n = 75 and α = 0.2."
